<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 18:18:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>史蒂文·马登因特朗普领导下的关税担忧而减少从中国采购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/steven-madden-cut-sourcing-china-tariff-worries-under-trump-2024-11-07/</link><description>史蒂文·马登(Steven Madden)高管周四表示，在唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)赢得美国总统大选后，该公司正在迅速将产品采购从中国转移到其他国家。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/steven-madden-cut-sourcing-china-tariff-worries-under-trump-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国火星车帮助寻找古代火星海岸线的证据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rover-helps-find-evidence-ancient-martian-shoreline-2024-11-07/</link><description>在中国祝融号火星车的帮助下，科学家们收集到了新的证据，证明火星在数十亿年前曾是海洋的家园，与今天干燥荒凉的世界相去甚远。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rover-helps-find-evidence-ancient-martian-shoreline-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国上市电视制造商因付款问题暂停俄罗斯工厂的生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-listed-tv-maker-halts-work-russian-factory-over-payment-issues-2024-11-07/</link><description>一家在中国上市的飞利浦、夏普和索尼电视机制造商周四告诉路透社，由于与外国供应商的备件付款问题，该工厂已停止其位于圣彼得堡附近的俄罗斯工厂的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-listed-tv-maker-halts-work-russian-factory-over-payment-issues-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国银行将从特朗普领导下的宽松资本和合并政策中获益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-gain-looser-capital-merger-policies-under-trump-2024-11-07/</link><description>行业专家和分析师表示，随着前总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，共和党监管机构预计将放宽资本规则和合并审批，银行业预计将赢得巨大胜利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-gain-looser-capital-merger-policies-under-trump-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>意大利削减汽车行业支持以避免资助中国制造的汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-cuts-automotive-industry-support-avoid-funding-cars-made-china-2024-11-07/</link><description>意大利经济部长周四表示，意大利政府计划削减此前用于支持该国汽车工业的资金，以避免资助中国制造的汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 14:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-cuts-automotive-industry-support-avoid-funding-cars-made-china-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>奥迪在中国推出无四环标志的新电动汽车品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-unveils-new-ev-brand-china-without-four-ring-logo-2024-11-07/</link><description>奥迪周四在中国推出了一个新的电动汽车品牌，该品牌的汽车将仅使用奥迪名称，而不是其标志性的四环标志，此举旨在吸引全球最大汽车市场的年轻客户。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-unveils-new-ev-brand-china-without-four-ring-logo-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国逮捕涉嫌向中国提供军事情报的美国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-us-citizen-suspected-offering-military-intel-china-2024-11-07/</link><description>德国联邦检察官办公室周四在一份声明中表示，德国逮捕了一名涉嫌向中国提供美国军方情报的美国公民，这些情报是他在为驻德部队工作时获得的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-us-citizen-suspected-offering-military-intel-china-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>塔塔钢铁首席执行官表示，长期从中国进口可能会影响印度钢铁行业的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/prolonged-chinese-imports-may-hit-indian-steel-industrys-investments-tata-steel-2024-11-07/</link><description>塔塔钢铁公司首席执行官周四对路透表示，印度从中国进口的钢铁价格“不公平”，长期发货可能会损害国内钢铁行业的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:53:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/prolonged-chinese-imports-may-hit-indian-steel-industrys-investments-tata-steel-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：联合利华、宝洁公司面临特朗普威胁对墨西哥征收关税的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/unilever-procter-gamble-face-risk-trumps-threatened-mexico-tariffs-2024-11-07/</link><description>路透社独家看到的数据显示，如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普继续威胁对墨西哥征收关税，宝洁和联合利华等大型包装商品公司将面临风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/unilever-procter-gamble-face-risk-trumps-threatened-mexico-tariffs-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>Vendee Globe首位中国水手旨在激励后代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/first-chinese-sailor-vendee-globe-aims-inspire-future-generations-2024-11-07/</link><description>周日，在第 10 届 Vendee Globe 帆船比赛中，12 名非法国船长中的徐靖坤将成为首位不间断独自环球航行的中国水手，尽管他在 20 岁时失去了左臂。 12.</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:46:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/first-chinese-sailor-vendee-globe-aims-inspire-future-generations-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>泰国总理在中国峰会期间会见缅甸军政府首脑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-meets-myanmar-junta-chief-sidelines-summit-china-2024-11-07/</link><description>周四，泰国总理白东坦·西那瓦 (Paetongtarn Shinawatra) 在中国举行的地区峰会期间会见了缅甸军政府首脑，这是一位正在应对国内内战的将军罕见的海外访问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:58:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-meets-myanmar-junta-chief-sidelines-summit-china-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储和英国央行决定，美国众议院等待，德国感到不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-07/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>高通推动智能手机市场复苏，中国手机推出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-advances-smartphone-market-revival-chinese-handset-launches-2024-11-07/</link><description>高通公司股价周四上涨 4%，此前这家芯片设计公司强劲的季度营收预测激发了投资者对中国主导的智能手机市场复苏的乐观情绪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-advances-smartphone-market-revival-chinese-handset-launches-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国农民支持特朗普，但面临中国关税威胁的痛苦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-farmers-back-trump-face-pain-china-tariff-threats-2024-11-07/</link><description>美国农民希望从当选总统唐纳德·特朗普那里得到一些他的贸易政策意味着他不太可能实现的东西：增加进入最大大豆进口国中国市场的准入。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-farmers-back-trump-face-pain-china-tariff-threats-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国农产品生产商准备应对特朗普政府对中国出口的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-farm-producers-brace-hit-exports-china-trump-administration-2024-11-07/</link><description>美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普再次打击对华农产品出口，美国农业生产商正在为新一轮贸易战的前景做好准备，但他们表示，尽管任何新关税都会造成损害，但他们感觉准备得更好。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 10:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-farm-producers-brace-hit-exports-china-trump-administration-2024-11-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>